name: Arthur Hayes
content: "This Is Fine" — essay on why $BTC is predicting an AI-adoption driven financial crisis which will be "solved" with printed money. Bitcoin's divergence from Nasdaq is the "global fiat liquidity fire alarm."

name: Arthur Hayes
content: Warm up that printer, Powell. Blue Owl permanently halted redemptions for retail investors in its private credit fund — a sign of growing liquidity crunch.

name: Colin Wu
content: Crypto VC fundraising last quarter equaled just 12% of Q2 2022 level. New fund formation fell to five-year low. 85% of 2025 tokens trading below launch prices.
